CHAT.comment: Time is 1:17. Tape has 1:17 of blank space at beginning

both Chi and her sister are very silly throughout the interaction , and they giggle through long stretches of the transcript. The dinner hour is very confrontational , with Mot scolding both children often for lapses of table manners. In multiple instances , MOT will make an ultimatum or a threat (for example , regarding having apple pie for desert) , and then almost immediately reverse herself. Both children , for the most part , ignore Mot's threats. Chi and Mot discuss some activities which happened in school for a few moments , and there is a discussion of some of Mot's coworkers , but the vast majority of the interaction is negotiation about the food and how to eat it. During the conversation about the coworker , MOT sarcastiaclly threatens to give the two girls away to the coworker in question , to which the girls respond enthusiastically and sarcastically that they'd like to go. At one point , Chi spells the word fun out of butter pats , which Mot first says is inappropriate use of food , and then says is cute. Fat comes home towards the tail end of the transcript , and Mot explains that the girls have been giggling all night and she doesn't know why.
